    "The Great Teacher Award from the Society of Columbia Graduates was bestowed upon him in 1990.": [],
    "In 2000 Brilliant published <em>My Laoco\u00f6n: Alternative Claims in the Interpretation of Artworks</em>, in which, in contrast to <a href=\"/bieberm\">Margarete Bieber</a> and her book on the Laoco\u00f6n, took a pluralistic view of its interpretatioin, denying that a definitive interpretation of work was possible.": [],
    "<em>Gesture and Rank in Roman Art</em> Brilliant asserted in 1993, was one of the first semiotic study in modern art history (Brilliant, 1994).": [],
